Package: brsm
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Response Surface Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Arian", "Alai",
      email = "aalai4@nebraska.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Tools for analyzing posterior distributions of quadratic response surfaces
    from Bayesian model fits. Provides functions for computing stationary points,
    ridge analysis, steepest ascent paths, and visualization of response surfaces
    with full posterior uncertainty quantification.
